Package: gluey
Title: Markdown Text Generation with Enhanced Templates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Robin", "Shannon", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate markdown text using the familiar syntax of 'glue' with
    enhanced templating features. Unlike 'cli' which produces styled console
    output, 'gluey' outputs plain markdown text, making it ideal for document
    generation in R Markdown and Quarto documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports:
    glue,
    uuid,
    pander,
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    checkmate,
    cli
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
